  <p class="vc-trust-note">
    <a href="https://sam.gov/entity/H8NGXEYE2HH8" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="vc-trust-link">Verify on SAM.gov →</a>
    <span class="vc-trust-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
    <a href="/governance/" class="vc-trust-link">Financial transparency →</a>
